   attacks involve the collision, denial of sleep, and selfish attack. The
   collision attack and denial of sleep attacks are researched and handled
   for MAC over the WBANs. However, selfish attack is not properly
   addressed. In this paper, we propose a selfish detection medium access
   control (SDMAC) algorithm against selfish attack in WBAN. Here the
   adversary nodes have advantage over legitimate nodes on MAC protocols
   that uses the resources wrongly, which leads to energy consumption in
   sensor nodes, proposed algorithm detects the fake node and blocks the
