Abstract = {One of key attributes of WBAN is to extend the network lifetime, which
   can be achieved by adjusting the wakeup and sleep modes of the sensor
   nodes. Traditional low-power methods such as channel polling and
   periodic duty cycling are unable to satisfy WBANs requirements due to
